---
layout: base.njk
title: Misconduct Comedy - Philadelphia's Best Stand-Up Shows
metaTitle: Misconduct Comedy
metaDescription: Come see the funniest stand-up show in the heart of Center City with Philly and NYC's best comedians! Tickets sell fast, Get yours now!
permalink: /index.html
generateShowSchema: true
---

<!-- Hero Section -->
<section class="hero">
    <div class="hero-overlay"></div>
    <div class="hero-content">
        <img src="/Misconduct Comedy Logo with Border - 750px.png" alt="Misconduct Comedy Logo" class="hero-logo">
        <h1>PHILLY'S FUNNIEST<br>LIVE COMEDY SHOW</h1>
        <p>Need date night plans? Or just a fun hang with friends? Misconduct Comedy has got you covered with Philly's best comedians in a cozy venue.</p>
    </div>
</section>

<!-- Shows Section -->
<section class="shows-section">
    <h2>UPCOMING SHOWS</h2>
    
    {%- for show in collections.showsByDate -%}
    <div class="show-card{% if show.data.ticketAvailability == 'https://schema.org/SoldOut' %} show-card-disabled{% endif %}">
        <div class="card-content">
            <div class="show-image">
                {% if show.data.images and show.data.images.length %}
                <img src="{{ show.data.images[0].src }}" alt="{{ show.data.images[0].alt or show.data.title }}">
                {% endif %}
            </div>
            <div class="show-info">
                <h3><a href="{{ show.url }}" style="color: #fff; text-decoration: none;">{{ show.data.title }}</a></h3>
                <div class="show-details">
                    {% if show.data.showType %}<span>{{ show.data.showType }}</span>{% endif %}
                    {% if show.data.ageRestriction %}<span>{{ show.data.ageRestriction }}</span>{% endif %}
                </div>
                <h4>{{ show.data.startDate | showDate }}</h4>
            </div>
            <div class="show-tickets">
                {% if show.data.ticketAvailability == "https://schema.org/InStock" and show.data.ticketUrl %}
                <a href="{{ show.data.ticketUrl }}" class="btn-tickets" target="_blank" onclick="gtag('event', 'ticket_click', {'event_category': 'Tickets', 'event_label': '{{ show.data.title }}', 'transport_type': 'beacon'});">BUY TICKETS{% if show.data.ticketPrice %} - ${{ show.data.ticketPrice }}{% endif %}</a>
                {% elif show.data.ticketAvailability == "https://schema.org/PreOrder" %}
                <span class="coming-soon">COMING SOON</span>
                {% elif show.data.ticketAvailability == "https://schema.org/SoldOut" %}
                <span class="coming-soon">SOLD OUT</span>
                {% else %}
                <span class="coming-soon">COMING SOON</span>
                {% endif %}
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
    {%- else -%}
    <p style="text-align: center; color: #aaa; padding: 2rem;">No shows scheduled yet. Check back soon!</p>
    {%- endfor -%}
</section>

<!-- About Section -->
<section class="about-section">
    <h2>ABOUT MISCONDUCT COMEDY</h2>
    <div class="about-intro">
        <p>Misconduct Comedy brings you Philadelphia's best stand-up comedy shows in the heart of Center City. Whether you're looking for the perfect date night or a fun outing with friends, our shows feature a mix of local favorites and touring headliners in an intimate, laid-back setting.</p>
    </div>
    <div class="features">
        <div class="feature">
            <div class="feature-icon">📍</div>
            <h3>The Venue</h3>
            <p><strong>Misconduct Tavern</strong><br><a href="https://maps.google.com/?q=1511+Locust+Street,+Philadelphia+PA+19102" target="_blank" class="venue-address">1511 Locust Street, Philadelphia PA 19102</a><br>Cozy bar setting with full drink menu and great atmosphere for comedy.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="feature">
            <div class="feature-icon">🎭</div>
            <h3>What to Expect</h3>
            <p>All of our shows run 75-90 minutes. Our showcases feature 5-7 talented local comedians and rising stars, while our Double Trouble Specials feature co-headliners doing extended 30-minute sets.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="feature">
            <div class="feature-icon">🎟️</div>
            <h3>Show Details</h3>
            <p><strong>Age:</strong> 21+<br><strong>Seating:</strong> First come, first served<br><strong>Doors:</strong> 30 minutes before showtime<br>Arrive early for best seats!<br><strong>Food/Drink:</strong> Full Menu is available 30 minutes before showtime</p>
        </div>
    </div>
</section>

<!-- FAQ Section -->
<section class="faq-section">
    <h2>FREQUENTLY ASKED QUESTIONS</h2>
    
    <div class="faq-item">
        <h3>Is there an age limit?</h3>
        <p>Yes, all attendees must be 21+ with a valid ID. This is strictly enforced at the door.</p>
    </div>

    <div class="faq-item">
        <h3>How long is the show?</h3>
        <p>All of our shows run between 75-90 minutes. There is no intermission.</p>
    </div>

    <div class="faq-item">
        <h3>Can I bring a group?</h3>
        <p>Absolutely! Groups are welcome. Since seating is first come, first served, we recommend arriving early to ensure your group can sit together.</p>
    </div>

    <div class="faq-item">
        <h3>Is there an item minimum?</h3>
        <p>There is a 2-item minimum and a bartender will be available for patrons to order food & drinks.</p>
    </div>

    <div class="faq-item">
        <h3>Can I buy tickets at the door?</h3>
        <p>We recommend purchasing tickets in advance as many shows sell out. If tickets are available, they may be purchased at the door for an additional fee.</p>
    </div>

    <div class="faq-item">
        <h3>If it's sold out, can I still attend?</h3>
        <p>Yes! We will be offering a small amount of tickets available at the door for $20, however we cannot guarantee that your party will be seated together.</p>
    </div>

    <div class="faq-item">
        <h3>What is the refund policy?</h3>
        <p>All sales are final. No refunds or exchanges. If you cannot attend, you may be able to receive a refund by contacting us at hausofcomedy@gmail.com.</p>
    </div>

    <div class="faq-item">
        <h3>Where can I park?</h3>
        <p>Street parking is available in the area, and there are several paid parking garages nearby. We recommend arriving with extra time to find parking.</p>
    </div>
</section>

